<h4 class="mb-3">Penerapan Fuzzy Mamdani</h4>
<h6 class="mb-3">Variabel Persentase ABC</h6>
<div class="mb-3">
    <p>Ilustrasi variabel persentase ABC dapat dilihat pada grafik berikut:</p>
    <p>
        \[
        \mu[x]
        \]
    </p>
    <p>Rendah:</p>
    <p>
        \[
        \begin{cases}
        0 & x \geq 4 \\
        \frac{4-x}{4-2} & 2 \leq x \leq 4 \\
        1 & x \leq 2
        \end{cases}
        \]
    </p>
    <p>Sedang:</p>
    <p>
        \[
        \begin{cases}
        0 & x \leq 0 \text{ or } x \geq 4 \\
        \frac{x-2}{4-2} & 2 \leq x \leq 4 \\
        \frac{6-x}{6-4} & 4 \leq x \leq 6
        \end{cases}
        \]
    </p>
    <p>Tinggi:</p>
    <p>
        \[
        \begin{cases}
        0 & x \leq 4 \\
        \frac{x-4}{6-4} & 4 \leq x \leq 6 \\
        1 & x \geq 6
        \end{cases}
        \]
    </p>
    
    <div class="fuzzy-abc"></div>
</div>

<hr>
